    "description": "The STS Secure for Windows XP, Embedded XP is a FIPS 140-2 Level 1 software module, comprised of the Security Manager Application Service (SMA), Key Generator Application, and the AES NDIS Filter Driver, that runs on a general purpose computer. It is the basis for Inter-4's Tactinet networking technology. The primary purpose for the STS Secure software module is to provide data security for all network wireless/wired traffic. In addition to data in transit (DIT), file based encryption protects files transferred to/from the platform via external USB drives.",
